OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fstart to the evening but remaining
OL,7,Fdry. The cloud will break overnight
OL,8,Finland but linger around the coasts.
OL,9,FPatches of fog possible in any clear
OL,10,Fspells.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FSunny spells through the
OL,13,Fmorning and early afternoon. Turning
OL,14,Fcloudier later, with outbreaks of
OL,15,Fheavy rain or showers in the evening
OL,16,Fand overnight. Chance of thunder. Warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
